peMA.Kathisma21.text = "The Women with faith brought spices for You, O Lord. * They earnestly wished to anoint You, the Friend of man. * Then an Angel spoke to them * from the tomb, announcing, \"The Giver of life * and Lord has arisen, * after trampling Hades and death.\""

